text: George Kenneth Robert McKinley (born 3 November 1993) is a cricketer from Larne, Northern Ireland, who has played at Larne Grammar School, Larne town and Ballymena, then at first-class level for Loughborough MCC University. He debuted for them during the 2015 English season, having earlier played for the Ireland national under-19 side.(5 August 2013). "McKinley leads Ireland Under 19’s to comfortable win" – Cricket Ireland. Retrieved 27 June 2015.First-class matches played by Robert McKinley – CricketArchive. Retrieved 27 June 2015. He made his List A debut for Northern Knights in the 2017 Inter-Provincial Cup on 29 May 2017.
